{"tid":711167,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"最近多咗生死討論 嚟一齊歌頌死亡","createTime":"2018-06-21T10:24:32.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-14T04:08:32.000Z","uid":191450,"like":13,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"8faade465aa98b32016e8a4de1d2fd6f03cb8942","tid":711167,"uid":191450,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-21T10:24:32.000Z","msg":"莫札特 死亡係唯一忠實嘅朋友<br />\n古希臘人話 人世第二美好嘅係 人終有一死(第一美好嘅係從來無出世過)<br />\n死亡係唯一可以確定嘅嘢<br />\n終有一日會搵到你<br />\n煙火同櫻花 因只開放瞬間而美麗<br />\n生命如是<br />\n因為隨時都可能死 所以先可以安心噉活著<br />\n對實上熱愛死亡嘅人 往往熱愛生命<br />\n歌頌死亡 所以要歌頌生命<br />\n對生命厭惡嘅人 死亡只係被迫嘅選擇<br />\n佢對睇唔到其他嘅選擇<br />\n但如果佢識得歌頌死亡 發現死亡常伴身伴<br />\n佢會發現人生其實有無限嘅選擇(除咗不死)<br />\n請一齊歌頌死亡 歌頌生命"},{"pid":"8e83ea685e7ba5fee59906452c4e0edf3a0ed859","tid":711167,"uid":191450,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-21T10:43:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dbd8da278433db3565bbbaa078b57a36bb0dcd95","tid":711167,"uid":29080,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-21T10:48:31.000Z","msg":"ok"},{"pid":"718125689e7b47a1e991f5d97df133970b4d581b","tid":711167,"uid":123456,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-21T10:51:54.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">奶波more行得太前<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> </span>"},{"pid":"f29324c5ab53bf537866210ced4bfc5cbad79745","tid":711167,"uid":191338,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-21T10:58:38.000Z","msg":"香港人冇時間思考生死平衡<br />\n打工仔日日返工做到無停手<br />\n收工就去食飯睇戲拍拖屌閪<br />\n好多年輕一代都做左慾便器<br />\n一有時間就玩手遊<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2e397d2c9446b7b68928b669652bcd0b4595d757","tid":711167,"uid":191450,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"f29324c5ab53bf537866210ced4bfc5cbad79745","tid":711167,"uid":191338,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-0